text: Automatically obtained when the first 28‌[PS3 only]/50‌[PS4 & PS Vita only] trophies after this one have been obtained.
Punch a tree until a block of Wood pops out.
Pick up a log from the ground.
Craft a workbench with four blocks of Wooden Planks.
Pick up a crafting table from the inventory's crafting field output or a crafting table output.
Use Planks and Sticks to make a Pickaxe.
Pick up any type of pickaxe from a crafting table output.
Construct a Furnace out of eight Cobblestone blocks.
Pick up a furnace from a crafting table output.
Pick up an iron ingot from a furnace output.
Pick up any type of hoe from a crafting table output.
Pick up bread from a crafting table output.
Bake a Cake using: Wheat, Sugar, Milk and Eggs.
Pick up a cake from a crafting table output.
Pick up a pickaxe from a crafting table output that is not a wooden pickaxe.
Pick up a cooked fish from a furnace output. Doesn't work if the furnace is hooked up to a hopper, as the player is not getting the item directly from the furnace.
Travel by Minecart to a point at least 500m in a single direction from where you started.
Travel by minecart to a point at least 500 blocks from where the player started. Distance is measured in a straight line.
Use planks and sticks to make a Sword.
Pick up any type of sword from a crafting table output.
Kill a hostile mob or one of the following neutral mobs: enderman, zombie pigman, spider, cave spider.
Pick up leather from the ground.
Use a Saddle to ride a Pig, and then have the Pig get hurt from fall damage while riding it.
Be riding a pig (e.g. using a saddle) when it hits the ground with a fall distance greater than 5.
This does not have to be in a single game, so multiple games or reloading old saves does count toward this achievement.
Construct one type of each tool.
Construct one pickaxe, one shovel, one axe, and one hoe.
Pick up a dispenser from a crafting table output.
Cook and eat a Pork Chop.
Play for 100 Minecraft days, which is equivalent to 33 hours in real time.
Kill a Skeleton with an Arrow from more than 50 meters.
Use a launched arrow to kill a skeleton, wither skeleton, or a stray from 50 or more blocks away, horizontally.
Acquire Diamonds with your iron tools.
Pick up a diamond from the ground.
Destroy a Ghast with a Fireball.
Kill a ghast using a ghast fireball.
Relieve a Blaze of its rod.
Pick up a blaze rod from the ground.
Pick up a potion from a brewing stand potion slot. An already-created potion placed and removed qualifies.
Pick up an enchantment table from a crafting table output.
Deal nine hearts of damage in a single hit.
Damage can be dealt to any mob, even those that do not have nine hearts of health overall.
Build some Bookshelves to improve your Enchantment Table.
Pick up a bookshelf from a crafting table output.
Visit any 17 biomes. Does not have to be in a single world.
Breed two cows or two mooshrooms.
Drop a diamond. Another player or a mob must then pick up this diamond.
Mine or buy 30 emeralds from a villager.
Craft and place a Flower Pot.
Eat a piece of rotten flesh while starving (zero hunger points).
Use Shears to obtain Wool from a Sheep.
All the colors of wool do not have to be in the inventory at the same time, but must have been picked up by the player once.
Swim in Lava while having the Fire Resistance effect.
Mine 1,728 Cobblestone and place it in a Chest.
A player must mine 1,728 cobblestone and place 1,728 cobblestone, or 27 stacks, in a chest. The cobblestone placed in the chest does not have to be the same cobblestone that was mined.
Smelt Wood Trunks using Charcoal to make more Charcoal.
Play a Music Disc in a Jukebox.
Wear a full suit of Iron Armor.
Throw a splash potion of weakness at a zombie villager and give it a golden apple (by facing the zombie and pressing the use button with a golden apple in your hand).
Be within a 100.9×100.9×103.5 cuboid centered on the Wither when it is spawned.
Be within a 100.9×100.9×203.5 cuboid centered on the Wither when it drops the nether star.
Create and fully power a Beacon.
Be within a 20×20×14 cuboid centered on the pyramid when the beacon block realizes it is fully powered.
Dye all 4 unique pieces of Leather Armor.
Bounce 30 blocks upward off a Slime Block.
Win a public Battle mini game.
Win 3 public Battle games in a row.
Take 100 damage in a round of a public Battle game.
Kill 2 players in a round of public Battle mini game using a bow and arrow.
Kill a player while you are starving in a Battle mini game.
Open every chest in a Battle mini game arena in one round.
Collect Dragon's Breath in a Glass Bottle.
Have a dragon's breath bottle in your inventory.
Use a Elytra to fly through a 1 by 1 gab while moving faster than 40 m/s.
Dry a Sponge in a Furnace.
Drink a potion of water breathing that can last for 2 minutes or more, then jump into the water or sneak on a magma block underwater for 2 minutes.
Poison a Witch with a Splash Potion.
Throw a splash potion of poison at a witch (by facing the witch and pressing the use button).
Teleport over 100 meters from a single throw of an Ender Pearl.
Place a fully explored Map into an Item Frame.
Place 9 fully explored, adjacent Maps into 9 Item Frames in a 3 by 3 square.
The frames have to be on a wall, not the floor.
Kill a Mob while wearing the same type of Mob Head.
Win 3 rounds in a row after one of the opponents has won 2 rounds.
Win a single round of Snowball Tumble without throwing any Snowballs.
Hit a single Player with 25 Snowballs in a single public round.
Hit a Player with a Snowball while falling into the Lava.
Push three Players into Lava using Snowballs.
Push three players into lava using snowballs in a single public round.
Stay on the top layer while winning a round in a Snowball Tumble Mini Game.
Win a Tumble game whilst on the lowest layer in a Snowball Tumble Mini Game.
Levitate up 50 blocks from the attacks of a Shulker.
Dye your bed a different color.
Use the Totem of Undying to cheat death.
Have the totem of undying in your hand when you die.
Have the totem of undying in a hotbar slot when you die.
So I Got That Going for Me...
Lead a Caravan containing at least 5 Llamas.
Walk across the surface of a deep ocean by freezing the water with Frost Walker boots.
One Pickle, Two Pickle, Sea Pickle, Four
Place four Sea Pickles in one block.
Use a Dried Kelp block as fuel in a furnace.
Place a conduit in a valid prismarine/sea lantern structure to activate it.
Eat nothing but Kelp for 3 days.
Eat dried kelp once; in the following three in-game days, eat nothing but dried kelp.
Stay underwater for one full day without using potions.
Spend 20 minutes underwater without any air.
Feed a dolphin raw cod and have it lure you to treasure.
Use a hopper to move an item from a chest minecart to a chest
Connect 3 Chests to a single furnace using 3 Hoppers
Push a piston with a piston, then pull the original piston with that piston
Breed a mule from a horse and a donkey
Use Riptide to give yourself a boost.
Obtain a trident enchanted with Riptide and launch yourself any distance with it.
Collect any fish in a bucket.
Use a water bucket on any fish mob to collect it.
Build a tower of Scaffolding that reaches the maximum build height.
Receive a gift in the morning from a tamed Cat.
The gift must be picked up from the ground.
Name a Shulker Box with an Anvil.
Craft a Banner using an Enchanted Apple.
Visit all ocean biomes except the deep warm ocean/legacy frozen ocean (as they are unused).
Trade for the best possible price.
Trade after you got Hero of the Village effect applied
Use a Grindstone to get experience from an enchanted item.
I've got a bad feeling about this
Ring the bell with a hostile enemy in the village.
Walk in a village with the Bad Omen effect applied.
Added the first 20 achievements. The PlayStation editions have an additional trophy.
Added 30 additional achievements, leading to a total of 50 (or 51 on the PlayStation editions).
The description of Adventuring Time has now been changed from "Discover 17 of the 23 different biomes" to "Discover 17 of the 40 different biomes".
Added 6 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 56.
Added 6 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 62.
Added 18 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 80.
Added 7 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 87.
Added 6 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 93.
Added 6 additional trophies, bringing the total up to 100.
Added 5 additional trophies, bringing the total up to 105.
Added 6 additional trophies, bringing the total up to 111.
Added 18 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 49.
Added 8 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 57.
Added 2 additional achievements, bringing the total up to 59.
